                    </div>
                    <span>This is mostly a list of why people can't create. The book provides few techniques to boost creativity. However, the blocking mechanisms are clearly explained. Identifying the problems is the path to a solution.... <br>I will look around to find books that describe some methodology to create more effectively.</span>
                  
